! Urxvt
! Font, see fc-list(1), live testing fonts with `printf '\e]710;%s\007' "xft:Terminus:pixelsize=12"`
! See live urxvtc by: `urxvtc -fn "xft:Terminus:pixelsize=12"`
URxvt*font:                         xft:Menlo:style=Regular, xft:Meslo GSDZ NFxft:Menlo Nerd Font:style=Regular, xft:Roboto, xft:DejaVu Sans Mono, xft:Unifont, xft:NotoColorEmoji, xft: Noto Emoji:size=
Urxvt.letterSpace:                  0

